name: Lucky Noodles
address: Aseana Avenue Entertainment City, Paranaque, Luzon 1701 Philippines
about: Fortune has shone on this haven for Asian gastronomy with its sumptuous soups, noodles, rice dishes, and traditional Asian specialties that pay homage to the various food festivals across the region. The open kitchen with a dining counter allows you to watch our chefs in action and whet your appetite for our Asian comfort food. Located directly off the casino floor, this quick and casual retreat is always buzzing with energy, a perfect venue for patrons 21 years and above to cool down and take a breather in between games. It is open 24 hours a day so you'll always have a chance to indulge.

about: Vikings Luxury Buffet is a contemporary and stylish restaurant that overlooks the majestic Manila Bay through its' vast windows. At Vikings, we are redefining the concept of buffet by incorporating show kitchens in our dining area to show our guests how our professionally trained chefs prepare dishes beyond expectations. We have an international buffet spread that is being constantly changed to make our valued guests to have something to look forward to (from freshly picked seafood to prime ribs, freshly made gourmet pizzas to local favorites), truly an epicurean epiphany.
